"title": "2045: Jesus Christ, knowledge of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2045: jesus christ, knowledge of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ has perfect insight into God's purposes and into human nature by reason of his intimate relationship with the Father, but he has accepted limited knowledge as a consequence of his humanity.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's knowledge of his Father</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:27\">MAT 11:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:22\">LUK 10:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:29\">JHN 7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:26\">JHN 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:55\">JHN 8:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:15\">JHN 10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:41-John11:42\">JHN 11:41–11:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:15\">JHN 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:25\">JHN 17:25</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's complete knowledge</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:30\">JHN 16:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:17\">JHN 21:17</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's foreknowledge of events</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's knowledge of his mission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:14\">JHN 8:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:3\">JHN 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:28\">JHN 16:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:4\">JHN 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:28\">JHN 19:28</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's knowledge of his death and resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:18-Matt20:19\">MAT 20:18–20:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:33-Mark10:34\">MRK 10:33–10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31-Luke18:33\">LUK 18:31–18:33</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's knowledge of his betrayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:64\">JHN 6:64</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:20-Matt26:25\">MAT 26:20–26:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:17-Mark14:20\">MRK 14:17–14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:11\">JHN 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:18\">JHN 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21-John13:26\">JHN 13:21–13:26</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's knowledge of the disciples' desertion and Peter's denial</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:31-Matt26:34\">MAT 26:31–26:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:27-Mark14:30\">MRK 14:27–14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:31-Luke22:34\">LUK 22:31–22:34</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's knowledge of human beings</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows every human heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:24-John2:25\">JHN 2:24–2:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:24\">ACT 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:23\">REV 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ discerns evil thoughts and motives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:18\">MAT 22:18</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:15\">MRK 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:23\">LUK 20:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:3-Matt9:4\">MAT 9:3–9:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:6-Mark2:8\">MRK 2:6–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:21-Luke5:22\">LUK 5:21–5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:14-Matt12:15\">MAT 12:14–12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:24-Matt12:25\">MAT 12:24–12:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:15-Luke11:17\">LUK 11:15–11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:7-Luke6:8\">LUK 6:7–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:42\">JHN 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:15\">JHN 6:15</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows those whose faith is not genuine</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:21–7:23</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows people's situations and needs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:47-John1:49\">JHN 1:47–1:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:34\">MRK 6:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:5\">LUK 19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:16-John4:19\">JHN 4:16–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:28-John4:29\">JHN 4:28–4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:6\">JHN 5:6</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's knowledge of believers</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows those who are his</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14\">JHN 10:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:15-John20:16\">JHN 20:15–20:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:19\">2TI 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows those who call on him in faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:24-Mark5:34\">MRK 5:24–5:34</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:18-Matt9:22\">MAT 9:18–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43-Luke8:48\">LUK 8:43–8:48</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:5\">MRK 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:20\">LUK 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows believers' deeds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:2\">REV 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:42\">MAT 10:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:41\">MRK 9:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:37-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:37–25:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:3\">REV 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:19\">REV 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:23\">REV 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows believer's needs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:48\">MRK 6:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:9-Rev2:10\">REV 2:9–2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:13\">REV 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:8\">REV 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows his disciples' misunderstandings and disputes</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:5-Matt16:8\">MAT 16:5–16:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:14-Mark8:17\">MRK 8:14–8:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:33-Mark9:35\">MRK 9:33–9:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:46-Luke9:48\">LUK 9:46–9:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:60-John6:61\">JHN 6:60–6:61</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:17-John16:19\">JHN 16:17–16:19</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ knows those who are half-hearted</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:2-Rev2:5\">REV 2:2–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1-Rev3:2\">REV 3:1–3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:15-Rev3:18\">REV 3:15–3:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's knowledge of the Scriptures</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:27\">LUK 24:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:4\">LUK 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:21\">MAT 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:3-Matt12:7\">MAT 12:3–12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:29-Matt22:32\">MAT 22:29–22:32</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:24-Mark12:27\">MRK 12:24–12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:34-Luke20:38\">LUK 20:34–20:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:37-Matt24:39\">MAT 24:37–24:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:26-Luke17:29\">LUK 17:26–17:29</a></p>\n<h2>Limitations of Jesus Christ's knowledge</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ acquired knowledge by usual human means</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:12\">MAT 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:13\">MAT 14:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:38\">MRK 6:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:21\">MRK 9:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:46\">LUK 2:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:52\">LUK 2:52</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:35\">JHN 9:35</a></p>\n<h3>Things that Jesus Christ did not know on account of his humanity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:36\">MAT 24:36</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32\">MRK 13:32</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:7\">ACT 1:7</a></p>",
